setDetails.setDescription:
The Blockschain DeFi Index is a collection of cryptocurrency projects that encompass all sectors of decentralized finance. 

Sectors Include:
Metaverse and Gaming
Lending
Automated Market Makers
Decentralized Exchanges
Storage
Indexing
Oracles
Wrapped Tokens

This index allows you to invest in 15 different DeFi projects through the purchase of a single token. Built on Polygon to make the investment process cheaper and more convenient.
Rebalancing takes place when necessary to maximize potential profit.
setDetails.managerDescription: At Blockschain, we create diversified token indexes that easily allow you to invest in decentralized finance convieniently with low fees.
